:

1. *Zamolio* je majku da mu dozvoli da ide u šetnju. (He asked his mother to allow him to go for a walk.)
2. Ona je *zamolila* njega da joj pomogne. (She asked him to help her.)
3. *Zamoljeno* je da se svi pridržavaju propisa. (It was requested that everyone adhere to the regulations.)
4. Ona je *zamoljivala* roditelje da joj kupe novi telefon. (She was pleading with her parents to buy her a new phone.)
5. *Zamolio* sam ga da izađe iz moje sobe. (I asked him to leave my room.)